Winnie Madikizela-Mandela was admitted to the Milpark hospital on Wednesday, a spokesperson confirmed.Madikizela-Mandela has been admitted for observation, her spokesperson, Victor Dlamini, said&nbsp;on Thursday.He was unable to provide any additional information.Madikizela-Mandela stayed briefly at the Milpark Hospital in December for observation.In April, she was in a hospital after undergoing back surgery. &mdash;&nbsp;News24